		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You combine disciplined martial training with sheer adrenaline-pumping ferocity to gain the edge in battle. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your Strength or Constitution score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your fighter levels count as berserker levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.q1v63h8j4a87n3t0]{Extra Attack} feature.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain proficiency with improvised weapons.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You can use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.9txksq0xfe5sgspl]{Furious Critical} with any one-handed weapon that lacks the dual-wielding property.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When you score a critical hit with a mastered maneuver, the target suffers disadvantage on its save (if any) against your Furious Critical.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
